# Context

This data set contains two class of images Buildings and Forests. This can be best utilized in a binary classification problem set in computer vision.

## Note: I got this data from[ Intel Image Classification](url), but I only chose two classes for binary classification

# Content 

This data contains around 5k images, And I spilt the data for two directory 
training_set contains around a 4k images
test_set contains around a 1k images

# Acknowledgements
Thanks to https://datahack.analyticsvidhya.com for the challenge and Intel for the Data

Photo by [Jan Böttinger on Unsplash](url)
